---
const title = '自鎖式矯正是什麼';
const subtitle = '自鎖式矯正器不論是在外觀、清潔、舒適性上，都為患者帶來更多好處。';
const content1 =
  '自鎖式矯正器與一般矯正器特別之處，在於黏在牙齒上面一顆顆的矯正器，是經過特殊設計，增加可以開閉的掀蓋，利用掀蓋來固定矯正線，不需要在每個矯正器上面，再用鐵線或小橡皮圈固定。';
const content2 =
  '看似小小的變化，卻能夠避免鐵線刮傷或破壞口腔組織，也可減少口腔內異物，提升牙齒清潔便利性，也因矯正的力量可以直接地傳達到牙齒上，進而提升矯正效率。';
---

<section id="visiting-environment" class="h-auto w-full scroll-mt-[80px]">
  <div class="w-full h-auto flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row items-center">
    <div class="w-full h-full md:w-[60%] flex flex-wrap px-4 md:pl-[100px]">
      <div class="w-full text-center md:text-left h-full max-h-[300px] my-auto py-12">
        <div class="text-center md:text-left">
          <p class="text-default font-bold tracking-[.2em] text-[20px] md:text-[28px] xl:text-[30px] mb-4">{title}</p>
          <p class="text-default tracking-[.2em] text-[12px] md:text-[12px] xl:text-[14px] mb-4">{content1}</p>
          <p class="text-default tracking-[.2em] text-[12px] md:text-[12px] xl:text-[14px] mb-4">{content2}</p>
          <span class="text-default font-bold tracking-[.2em] text-[16px] md:text-[16px] xl:text-[16px] underline my-4">
            {subtitle}
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full md:w-[40%] overflow-hidden flex items-center">
      <div class="w-full h-full text-left md:max-h-[500px] flex flex-row">
        <div class="w-10/12">
          <img class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="/assets/images/self-brace/explain.jpg" alt="" />
        </div>
        <div class="min-h-[300px] md:h-full w-2/12">
          <div class="ml-5 h-full w-[100px] bg-default-bg-0 -right-[480px] md:min-h-[500px]"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
